{"tid":1003030,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"流感肆虐　醫護大控訴","createTime":"2019-01-31T10:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T10:54:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d010a91be78bf9ae925f7539003c6e8a21ad20","tid":1003030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190131/20602999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F20602999&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2Fd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=eccdb3dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F20602999&h=7e20161d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190131/20602999</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月31日 <br />\n<br />\n流感肆虐　醫護大控訴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190131/large/19073230.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190131%2Flarge%2F19073230.jpg&h=532654ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n流感高峯期，公立醫院前線醫護忙個不停，甚至連吃飯、如廁的時間也沒有，特首林鄭月娥剛剛宣佈增加撥款五億元應對流感，究竟是否真的有效？新資源能否下放到前線？你是否做到一肚子氣想申訴？我們歡迎你投稿、投片、投相、投圖來《蘋果》電郵：health@appledaily.com，說一說病房環境有多惡劣，病人有多慘，工作安排多不人道，將真相告訴政府、醫管局高層及廣大市民。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n公院頻爆煲　政府欠承擔 (郭家麒)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n更制不公　身心俱疲 (伊利沙伯醫院護士)"}]}